{"tid":1262970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有團體往多國駐港總領事館請願　促外國不要干預香港事","createTime":"2019-06-28T02:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T03:50:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"71462128aee7b5d33787b36a3a8c5086f5b1e4ae","tid":1262970,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465495-20190628.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465495-20190628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=c6999c69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465495-20190628.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6a60098f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465495-20190628.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有團體在遮打花園集合前往美國、歐盟、英國和德國駐港總領事館請願，要求外國不要干預香港事務，發起人表示，現場有200人參與。<br />\n<br />\n團體高呼「反對外國勢力干預香港事務，香港事務香港人自己解決」口號，手持標語，沿花園道前往美國領事館。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，是透過網上號召集會，他表示，希望表達香港內部事務不容外國干預，認為是侮辱香港法治，被問到外國勢力是指甚麼，發言人表示，例如最近美國不尋常地發表言論，認為是別有用心。"},{"pid":"fdde5f6fff0fe0af031425b1011a80ee8e2b3519","tid":1262970,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"香港事務香港人自己解決<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"7ff51711c2b74a19be26698640741e37dc909135","tid":1262970,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"司法唔獨立仲法乜治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b236a4aad5744ea606288ac20a5b1a04faff10ed","tid":1262970,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"付live，可能已完<br />\n<br />\n【團體發起到多國領事館請願要求外國不要干預香港事務】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51c71008019660143